### 3) Propose → child `gene_genome` extending the parent

Rationale: Extend the parent from generic de novo PPI prediction to AlphaFold3-style biomolecular complex prediction that incorporates cell-type-specific PTM information, especially phosphorylation and other signaling-relevant modifications in cancer cells.

```action
