### 3) Propose → child gene_genome extending the parent

Rationale: The child study narrows the broad AI-conservation agenda into a testable interdisciplinary framework: remote sensing foundation models fused with indigenous ecological knowledge and local sensor data for early biodiversity-loss detection.

```action
{
  "tool": "propose",
  "gene_genome": {
